<span id="freeTextContainer7218703657689974815">Jessica is a typical 16-year-old girl, who happens to be born at midnight. This doesn’t mean anything to her until the day she moves with her family to Bixby. Soon she discovers that she and a few others, the Midnighters, are able to live one extra hour every midnight, while everyone else is frozen. This is all fun until she learns that they are not the only ones moving through midnight. Darklings and Slithers are coming after her and she has to be protected.<br/><br/>The first book is introducing us to t</span>
  <span id="freeText7218703657689974815" style="display:none">Jessica is a typical 16-year-old girl, who happens to be born at midnight. This doesn’t mean anything to her until the day she moves with her family to Bixby. Soon she discovers that she and a few others, the Midnighters, are able to live one extra hour every midnight, while everyone else is frozen. This is all fun until she learns that they are not the only ones moving through midnight. Darklings and Slithers are coming after her and she has to be protected.<br /><br />The first book is introducing us to this new midnight world and follows Jessica as she learns about her new powers.<br /><br />With wonderful characters and a thrilling story this book is one of my favourites.</span>
